{"tid":462262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蠢賊搶熱狗店　槍走火打中下面「小熱狗」求救","createTime":"2017-11-08T11:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T16:07:00.000Z","uid":19408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c6b0181dacef4b1bda8b78d8f6d810b1775b49","tid":462262,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"實在有夠蠢！美國一名少年持槍打劫一間熱狗店，結果在得手逃跑過程中，將手槍插到褲子裡時，槍枝不慎走火，不偏不倚射中他褲子裡的「小熱狗」，讓他痛得只好打電話報警求救，在醫院中直接被警方逮捕。<br />\n <br />\n據《芝加哥論壇報》報導，芝加哥一名19歲少年龐西（Terrion Pouncy）日前持槍搶劫一間24小時營業的熱狗店。當時他用黑色圍巾遮住臉，並揮舞槍枝要求店員交出收銀機裡的錢，以及兩人的手機與錢包，隨後迅速跑離現場。<br />\n <br />\n當龐西得手要逃走時，將槍插進褲子裡，沒想到槍枝意外擦槍走火，射中了他的GG跟大腿，讓他痛不欲生。雖然他忍著蛋蛋的哀傷逃走，但最後還是忍不住打電話報警求救，表示自己被槍射中。<br />\n <br />\n龐西隨後被送往醫院治療，但也讓警方輕鬆查出原委，並將他逮捕，將依搶劫和非法持有槍械移送法辦。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/806710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F806710&d=C7Nhrggf5fU%2FgAjPVu1CizA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a8553a57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/806710</a>"},{"pid":"e6c6e9f4dba458f13a222ca5959f6a07c9a1b977","tid":462262,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"放心！唔駛割包皮"},{"pid":"6f117cdbb2ebfbc346b0e6f3c5463ae4d6b8ae9b","tid":462262,"uid":11301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/222317_10bccc1d7e5c9c9bd907e1988a8ecdbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F222317_10bccc1d7e5c9c9bd907e1988a8ecdbc.jpg&h=14ad95b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b71ef920346d40283c064b4dfc25f6d6b2bba408","tid":462262,"uid":6086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"睇美劇成日見佢地d槍插落褲入面都覺得好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1999967deafcfef7e81e1ed05b6f3e60619765","tid":462262,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"想搵藉口堂皇自首姐"},{"pid":"6fd4500b56968084b21c7f77226cb805adaa2826","tid":462262,"uid":68219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇美劇成日見佢地d槍插落褲入面都覺得好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓 咩劇<br />\nholster同褲袋兩樣野黎"},{"pid":"6383c65bae4b8d33a238f482090afc55e0f410e5","tid":462262,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"有無爆頭"}]}